    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know there are people who care, but they only care because they feel obligated to. i see the look in their eyes when they visit... it's pity. they're just waiting for me to pass so they can finally stop worrying. i feel like i'm just stuck in this waiting room, watching life happen from a distance. it feels so much more dignified to have some kind of say in how it ends instead of just letting it drag on until i'm completely broken.",
